The package boost-parameter-python is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS parameter_python)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::parameter_python)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_parameter_python REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::parameter_python)
